'''点击劫持'''（{{lang|en|clickjacking}}）是一种在[[网页|网页]]中将[[恶意代码|恶意代码]]等隐藏在看似无害的内容（如[[按钮_(计算机)|按钮]]）之下，并诱使用户点击的手段。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/index.php/id;979405561|title=At Adobe's request, hackers nix 'clickjacking' talk|author=Robert McMillan|date=2008-09-17|publisher=PC World|accessdate=2008-10-08|archive-date=2015-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150717230102/http://www.pcworld.idg.com.au/article/260609/adobe_request_hackers_nix_clickjacking_talk/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://infotech.indiatimes.com/quickiearticleshow/3543527.cms|title=Beware, clickjackers on the prowl|author=Megha Dhawan|date=2008-09-29|publisher=India Times|accessdate=2008-10-08|archive-date=2009-07-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090724155021/http://infotech.indiatimes.com/quickiearticleshow/3543527.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2008/10/07/clickjacking_surveillance_zombie/ |title=Net game turns PC into undercover surveillance zombie |author=Dan Goodin |date=2008-10-07 |work=The Register |accessdate=2008-10-08 |archive-date=2018-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181204131742/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2008/10/07/clickjacking_surveillance_zombie/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/nf/20081008/bs_nf/62355 |title=Web Surfers Face Dangerous New Threat: 'Clickjacking' |author=Fredrick Lane |date=2008-10-08 |format= |work= |publisher=newsfactor.com |accessdate=2008-10-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013003436/http://news.yahoo.com/s/nf/20081008/bs_nf/62355 |archivedate=2008-10-13 |deadurl=yes }} </ref>该术语最早由雷米亚·格罗斯曼（{{lang|en|Jeremiah Grossman}}）与罗伯特·汉森（{{lang|en|Robert Hansen}}）于2008年提出。这种行为又被称为'''界面伪装'''（{{lang|en|UI redressing}}）。

点击劫持可以被看成是[[责任混淆问题|责任混淆问题]]（{{lang|en|confused deputy problem}}）的一个实例。<ref>[http://waterken.sourceforge.net/clickjacking/ The Confused Deputy rides again!] {{Wayback|url=http://waterken.sourceforge.net/clickjacking/ |date=20210224200352 }}, Tyler Close, October 2008</ref>

举例来说，如用户收到一封包含一段视频的[[电子邮件|电子邮件]]，但其中的“播放”按钮并不会真正播放视频，而是链入一购物网站。这样当用户试图“播放视频”时，实际是被诱骗而进入了一个购物网站。

通过在客户端安装[[NoScript|NoScript]]或NoClickjack扩展等手段可以防止点击劫持的发生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hackademix.net/2008/10/08/hello-clearclick-goodbye-clickjacking/ |title=Hello ClearClick, Goodbye Clickjacking |author=Giorgio Maone |date=2008-10-08 |publisher=hackademix.net |accessdate=2008-10-27 |archive-date=2021-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210305084104/https://hackademix.net/2008/10/08/hello-clearclick-goodbye-clickjacking/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

